modName: Skyrim Wayshrines Beyond Reach Patch Fix (2018) - DELETED
summary: Fix for the Beyond Reach patch for Skyrim Wayshrines (SWIFT) by Pharros.
descriptionHtml:
Changed an outdated dependency on arnima.esp to arnima.esm. Fixed all resulting errors. Scanned with merge plugins.

[quote]"[i]I give permission to any user who wishes to create fixes/patches for my mod as long as they credit me and include a link to my mod.[/i]"[/quote]
Obviously requires Pharros' mod located [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64201/]here[/url].

(I haven't been able to test it since I haven't started BR but if I know anything about TES5edit I'm pretty confident.)
